		    <p>A gymnast is training by hanging from two ropes attached to the ceiling, as shown in the figure. 
				The angles <m>\theta</m> and <m>\alpha</m> are different.  
				The mass of the gymnast is <m>75 \mathrm{~kg}</m>.  
				Determine the magnitude of the tension in each rope.</p>
